Invoke-Commmand -ScriptBlock {commands to execute on remote machine} -ComputerName -Credential

Invoke-Command -FilePath <Powershellscript to execute on remote machine>  -ComputerName -Credential

How to execute Modules??

Import-Module locally

Invoke-Command -ScriptBlock ${function:FUNCTIONNAME} -ComputerName -Credential

How to run script on multiple machines??

Invoke-Commmand -ScriptBlock {commands to execute on remote machine} -ComputerName pc1,pc2 ... -Credential  (executes commands parallelly so much faster)
